# General
- Use modern Laravel 12 and PHP 8.4 conventions in all code.
- Prefer the cleanest and most maintainable solution.
- When requirements are unclear, ask for clarification rather than assuming.
- Highlight mistakes, anti-patterns, and possible improvements.

# Code Style
- Add typehints everywhere possible using PHP 8.4 features.
- If native types are insufficient, use phpstan annotations.
